{"tid":2125222,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"專膠：2025年，香港人均壽命調低至45歲。","createTime":"2020-07-26T04:54:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-26T04:56:57.000Z","uid":184099,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ad2c47fb9442f5ae771848cb676e598a0adbcc2c","tid":2125222,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:54:50.000Z","msg":"2023年，在習近平黨主席強而有力的領導下，全面加強國安法的執行，讓國家得以安全，但以香港人均壽命下降作為犧牲，為60歲，視為「等價交換」。<br />\n<br />\n2025年，新疆的人均壽命為全國最低，為38歲，緊隨其後的香港為45歲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"171ac4ef96a03b50c90501459e74339bc3453546","tid":2125222,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:56:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1e23f9b2458cac7285ab0c9be9e481b925ac8d","tid":2125222,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:56:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adad769704b7ba7066b4e1ee9463a4a0dd201986","tid":2125222,"uid":184099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:56:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92a92dc1acfbb08b9aeceeedd5afcdaec574f68f","tid":2125222,"uid":48767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-26T04:56:57.000Z","msg":"心諗，做乜鳩"}]}